{
  "stem": "23350.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But when they came, when they rounded us all up in 1942, and he was holding the certificate in his hand.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the Gestapo took it in front of the burgermeister, took the paper, tore it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Shyster, you know they said, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "What did the certificate say?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It said that he had that Munter, Jacob Munter, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] is allowed-- is going to work in the gardens for the magistrate.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, my father didn't get paid or anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But thank God, he could get out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because this way we could get some butter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We could then get some eggs and things, food, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Till 1942.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in '42 they rounded us up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was working with the tailors already at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was another instance that was right in the beginning as well, when the burgermeister came with the secretary.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were going from place to place to take the inventory, what everyone owns, Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And especially people who owned land.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they came around to our house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I could see through the kitchen window him going down the steps to the yard down there with the secretary.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my mother was alone with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father was hiding in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He wouldn't come out at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father had a big beard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my sisters were out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was only me and my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my mother was starting like this, when she asked the burgermeister here, what do they want?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said, Mama, tell me exactly what we have got.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What should I tell them?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I will go down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She said, no, how can you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You're only a child.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
